# Architecture

- `src/features/<feature>/{components,hooks,api,types,__tests__}/`
- `src/shared/` for cross-feature primitives only.
- No cross-feature imports from `features/*/components` into other features.
- One responsibility per module. Co-locate tests.
- State: local first; React Query for server state; Redux only with justification.
- New abstractions require justification in the PR.
- Public seams must be typed end-to-end.
See `.opencode/agents/architecture.md`.